reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Bed Frame
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Lutown-Teen 14 Inch Full Size Bed Frame and I am extremely satisfied with my purchase. This bed frame has exceeded my expectations in terms of quality, durability, and overall design.Firstly, the build quality of this bed frame is exceptional. It is made from high-quality materials that feel sturdy and solid. The frame is well-constructed and does not wobble or squeak, providing a stable and comfortable sleeping experience. I appreciate the attention to detail in the design, as all the parts fit together seamlessly.The 14-inch height of the bed frame is perfect for me. It provides ample storage space underneath the bed, allowing me to keep my room organized and clutter-free. The frame also has a sleek and modern design that adds a touch of elegance to my bedroom decor.Another great feature of this bed frame is its easy assembly process. The instructions were clear and concise, and I was able to put it together by myself in under an hour. The frame comes with all the necessary tools and hardware, making the assembly hassle-free.In terms of comfort, the Lutown-Teen bed frame does not disappoint. It provides excellent support for my mattress, ensuring a restful night's sleep. The frame also has a noise-free design, which is a huge plus for light sleepers like me.Overall, I highly recommend the Lutown-Teen 14 Inch Full Size Bed Frame. It is a well-made, durable, and stylish bed frame that offers great value for its price. Whether you're looking for extra storage space or simply want to upgrade your bedroom decor, this bed frame is an excellent choice.

reviews.reviewText: Quality is great, no issues, good instructions, easily put together, looks fine, gives me storage for 8 to 10 small size moving boxes, out of site.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Was pretty easy to set up, I did have a few hiccups but that was user error and not paying attention to the direction of the pieces as I installed them. Took longer to unpackage the parts than it did to set it up. I got the taller one so I can use the underneath space for storage and it works great for that. I purchased a long bed skirt and you can't see anything underneath it. I have not experienced any squeaking, and it seems to be very sturdy. My bed does not slide on it's own(when sleeping, only when I am putting sheets and stuff on it, which honestly makes things easier for me. Overall, happy with my purchase.

reviews.reviewText: This platform bed frame is everything I hoped for.
